rows.label: fev06_110_125_msg0001
rows.name:
That was quite the grand funeral
ceremony.

rows.label: fev06_110_125_msg0002
rows.name:
It spoke volumes as to just how much
Fan was loved by her people.

rows.label: fev06_110_125_msg0003
rows.name:
The Goddess of Acedia won't be
an easy position to replace.

rows.label: fev06_110_125_msg0004
rows.name:
Hey, Rex. What are you going
to do from here on out?

rows.label: fev06_110_125_msg0005
rows.name:
If we're going to reach the World Tree,
we'll need the Pope's help, but...

rows.label: fev06_110_125_msg0007
rows.name:
His Holiness Marveni wishes to
speak with you. He is waiting
in the audience chamber.

rows.label: fev06_110_125_msg0008
rows.name:
That's perfect timing, then.
Maybe he wants to talk about
the World Tree?

rows.label: fev06_110_125_msg0009
rows.name: I am afraid I cannot say.

rows.label: fev06_110_125_msg0010
rows.name: Well, there is only one way to find out.

rows.label: fev06_110_125_msg0011
rows.name:
Let's get ourselves on over to
that audience chamber, then.
